01:39:20.872 --> 01:39:23.123
I really can't do this.
What are you doing...

1397
01:39:23.666 --> 01:39:25.709
Come here! Come here.

1398
01:39:25.793 --> 01:39:30.047
- Why aren't you wearing your chute?
- Because I have to secure the VIPs first.

1399
01:39:30.131 --> 01:39:34.343
Okay. I want you to listen very carefully
and memorize everything that I say.

1400
01:39:34.427 --> 01:39:37.387
Each chute has a GPS tracker so you
can be found by Search and Rescue.

1401
01:39:37.472 --> 01:39:39.598
Right next to that's a fabric webbing
called a bridle.

1402
01:39:39.682 --> 01:39:41.808
which holds the pin
that keeps the main container closed.

1403
01:39:41.893 --> 01:39:43.977
- Okay. are you listening?
- I can't hear what...

1404
01:39:44.062 --> 01:39:45.479
- Stop that!
- All right. All right.

1405
01:39:45.563 --> 01:39:48.023
All right. when the pilot chute inflates into the air.

1406
01:39:48.107 --> 01:39:50.275
it pulls the pin and opens the main.

1407
01:39:50.360 --> 01:39:52.402
Red's your backup. blue's your primary.

1408
01:39:52.487 --> 01:39:56.657
I want you to pull the blue.
I need you to pull it really hard!

1409
01:39:56.741 --> 01:39:59.576
Not now. we're on the plane.
you dumb-ass!

1410
01:40:02.497 --> 01:40:05.499
- He say good-bye?
- No. he didn't even say good-bye.

1411
01:40:05.917 --> 01:40:07.751
General. we're loaded and ready.

1412
01:40:07.835 --> 01:40:10.712
You give us the go. and we'll be ready
to press in five minutes.

1413
01:40:10.797 --> 01:40:13.632
- Excellent.
- Sir. you need to see this now.

1414
01:40:16.260 --> 01:40:18.345
- Have we checked these coordinates?
- Egypt. sir.

1415
01:40:18.429 --> 01:40:21.181
- They're airdropping in.
- You've got to be kidding me.

1416
01:40:21.265 --> 01:40:22.683
He knows something.

1417
01:40:22.767 --> 01:40:25.102
We need to be ready to back him up
if this thing goes hot.

1418
01:40:26.437 --> 01:40:27.521
Copy that.

1419
01:40:27.605 --> 01:40:30.107
CIA just got a hit on the boy.

1420
01:40:30.650 --> 01:40:32.693
100 miles from the location
on that little note there.

1421
01:40:32.777 --> 01:40:33.860
It's getting hotter.

1422
01:40:38.324 --> 01:40:40.951
It's gotta be around here somewhere.

1423
01:41:02.181 --> 01:41:04.182
You see the size of this?

1424
01:41:04.892 --> 01:41:07.310
- You see this?
- Spectacular.

1425
01:41:08.980 --> 01:41:11.440
Amazing. Look at that.

1426
01:41:21.659 --> 01:41:23.994
- It's here somewhere. guys.
- Yeah. why?

1427
01:41:24.078 --> 01:41:25.620
'Cause we're trusting Grandpa Blackbird

1428
01:41:25.705 --> 01:41:27.205
who doesn't even know
what planet he's on?

1429
01:41:27.290 --> 01:41:31.293
In his defense. this is the biggest
doorway I've ever seen in my entire life.

1430
01:41:32.044 --> 01:41:35.589
Okay. Well. that's great.
Let me do a quick search. all right?

1431
01:41:35.673 --> 01:41:37.257
Nope. Ever cross your mind. guys.

1432
01:41:37.341 --> 01:41:38.759
that archeologists have been here before?

1433
01:41:38.843 --> 01:41:39.926
There's nothing here.

1434
01:41:40.011 --> 01:41:42.387
Real life is heartbreak. despair. kid.

1435
01:41:42.472 --> 01:41:44.598
Sometimes you get to the end of the rainbow

1436
01:41:44.682 --> 01:41:46.850
and the leprechauns went
and booby-trapped it!

1437
01:41:46.934 --> 01:41:49.311
I'm listening to you?
You live with your mother!

1438
01:41:50.480 --> 01:41:52.606
- It's not over.
- It is over. It's done.

1439
01:41:52.690 --> 01:41:54.191
Why are we still listening to you.
little punk-ass?

1440
01:41:54.275 --> 01:41:56.318
I mean. what you ever done for us
except ding my rim?

1441
01:41:56.402 --> 01:41:58.361
Killed Megatron.
How about that?

1442
01:41:58.446 --> 01:41:59.488
Well. he didn't get the job done.

1443
01:41:59.572 --> 01:42:01.114
you know what I mean.
'cause he's back now...

1444
01:42:01.199 --> 01:42:04.117
- Are you scared?
- Scared? Scared of your ugly face!

1445
01:42:04.202 --> 01:42:06.620
I'm ugly?
Well. we're twins. you stupid genius!

1446
01:42:06.704 --> 01:42:08.455
Bring it. then! Get off me!

1447
01:42:08.539 --> 01:42:11.625
- I'll change your face around!
- I'll get all up in that ass!

1448
01:42:11.709 --> 01:42:13.126
Bring it!

1449
01:42:13.878 --> 01:42:15.045
Guys!

1450
01:42:16.380 --> 01:42:17.964
- You like the way that feels?
- That didn't hurt.

1451
01:42:18.049 --> 01:42:19.591
You like that. don't you?

1452
01:42:19.675 --> 01:42:22.052
- Come on. Bumblebee!
- Bumblebee. listen.

1453
01:42:28.726 --> 01:42:29.726
Now. that's rude.

1454
01:42:41.697 --> 01:42:43.657
Oh. my God. The symbols.

1455
01:42:44.909 --> 01:42:46.743
Bee! Shoot it.

1456
01:43:12.603 --> 01:43:15.272
- Check this out.
- Look at it.

1457
01:43:16.524 --> 01:43:17.524
Wow!

1458
01:43:17.608 --> 01:43:20.110
These are the bodies
Jetfire was talking about.

1459
01:43:20.653 --> 01:43:22.571
The tomb of the Primes.

1460
01:43:23.030 --> 01:43:26.783
Yo!

1461
01:43:40.798 --> 01:43:42.132
The Matrix.

1462
01:43:59.692 --> 01:44:03.278
No.

1463
01:44:05.656 --> 01:44:08.199
Thousands of years. turned to dust.

1464
01:44:08.826 --> 01:44:10.785
This isn't how it's supposed to end.

1465
01:44:10.870 --> 01:44:12.037
Hear that?

1466
01:44:16.584 --> 01:44:18.960
US Air Force! C-17s!

1467
01:44:19.045 --> 01:44:21.755
- What's a C-17?
- You can't bring him back. Sam.

1468
01:44:21.839 --> 01:44:25.425
- There's nothing left.
- Look! Look around you.

1469
01:44:25.509 --> 01:44:28.094
We didn't just go through everything
we went through for no reason at all.

1470
01:44:28.179 --> 01:44:29.596
to just have it end like this.

1471
01:44:29.680 --> 01:44:31.348
There is a reason that we are here.

1472
01:44:31.432 --> 01:44:35.310
The voices and the symbols in my head
led us here for a purpose.

1473
01:44:41.192 --> 01:44:43.485
Everyone's after me
because of what I know.

1474
01:44:45.780 --> 01:44:48.990
and what I know is that this is going to work.

1475
01:44:49.450 --> 01:44:52.494
- How do you know it's gonna work?
- Because I believe it.

1476
01:45:02.546 --> 01:45:04.881
You best let me out of this plane.

1477
01:45:15.434 --> 01:45:18.520
Dropping the big boy. Sam!

1478
01:45:25.653 --> 01:45:27.904
You think you can bring him back to life
with that pixie dust?

1479
01:45:27.989 --> 01:45:29.572
Absolutely. Let's go.

1480
01:45:39.667 --> 01:45:40.875
Go!

1481
01:45:41.711 --> 01:45:44.421
Let's move it.
Remember. they're friendlies.

1482
01:45:55.057 --> 01:45:56.599
Cover Optimus!

1483
01:45:59.562 --> 01:46:01.646
Secure the village.
Get those cases down here.

1484
01:46:01.731 --> 01:46:03.857
I need snipers and Stingers up high.

1485
01:46:03.941 --> 01:46:08.069
So. we just dropped off 10 tons of dead robot
in the middle of nowhere.

1486
01:46:08.154 --> 01:46:09.779
I hope this little kid know
what he's doing.

1487
01:46:09.864 --> 01:46:10.905
Yeah. me too.

1488
01:46:16.871 --> 01:46:20.081
Got a visual! Yellow team! Four clicks!

1489
01:46:23.377 --> 01:46:24.711
Pop flare!

1490
01:46:26.964 --> 01:46:29.591
- That's them. right there. See the flare?
- Right over there! See it?

1491
01:46:40.644 --> 01:46:41.811
Sam!

1492
01:46:54.158 --> 01:46:55.700
Oh. God. Please. God! Please.

1493
01:46:55.785 --> 01:46:57.410
Leo. stop freaking out. Stop freaking out.

1494
01:46:57.495 --> 01:46:58.912
Shut this guy up. huh?

1495
01:46:58.996 --> 01:47:01.414
- Please. just let me live. just let me live!
- Shut up and let him drive!

1496
01:47:01.499 --> 01:47:02.791
- Just stop screaming...
- All right. that's it!

1497
01:47:05.503 --> 01:47:06.961
I can't take that guy anymore.

1498
01:47:20.226 --> 01:47:22.310
Hide in the dust!
Use the dust!

1499
01:47:29.902 --> 01:47:31.861
We've got to split up.
Bumblebee. you're the decoy.

1500
01:47:31.946 --> 01:47:34.614
You lead the Decepticons away. all right?
I'm gonna get Optimus.

1501
01:47:34.698 --> 01:47:37.242
I'll help draw their fire
with Huey and Dewey there.

1502
01:47:37.326 --> 01:47:39.369
You get to those soldiers.

1503
01:47:40.496 --> 01:47:43.540
- I hope that dust works. kid.
- Thank you.

1504
01:47:47.336 --> 01:47:50.797
He's turning around. He's coming back.
He's coming back.

1505
01:47:51.549 --> 01:47:52.590
It's up to me.

1506
01:47:52.883 --> 01:47:55.552
One man. alone.
betrayed by the country he loves.

1507
01:47:55.636 --> 01:47:58.138
now its last hope
in their final hour of need.

1508
01:47:58.222 --> 01:48:01.891
Prepare to be driven like never before.
by the maestro.

1509
01:48:01.976 --> 01:48:04.978
- Hey. hey! Don't go nowhere! Drive.
- You'll never make it. kid.

1510
01:48:05.062 --> 01:48:07.522
- I'm coming with you.
- Bravery will only get you so far.

1511
01:48:07.606 --> 01:48:10.525
You tased me. okay?
You owe me! I'm going.

1512
01:48:10.609 --> 01:48:12.402
Okay. okay. That was a test.
You passed. All right?

1513
01:48:20.703 --> 01:48:24.122
That thing's got alien tattoos all over it.
That ain't Air Force.

1514
01:48:28.210 --> 01:48:30.378
- What the hell was that?
- Anyone copy?

1515
01:48:30.462 --> 01:48:32.505
- Anyone there? Who's up?
- Copy?

1516
01:48:32.590 --> 01:48:34.883
- Radio's down.
- It's dead. Comms are down.

1517
01:48:34.967 --> 01:48:36.301
EMP burst.

1518
01:48:36.677 --> 01:48:39.554
I see how this day is going
in this godforsaken desert.

1519
01:48:41.307 --> 01:48:42.348
Yes. sir?

1520
01:48:42.433 --> 01:48:45.268
- Major Lennox told me to pull the cord.
- I know. sir.

1521
01:48:45.352 --> 01:48:48.188
Well. what country am I in right now?

1522
01:48:48.272 --> 01:48:49.522
United States.

1523
01:48:49.607 --> 01:48:53.526
No. not the United States.
I'm from the United States.

1524
01:48:53.611 --> 01:48:56.279
I'm in the middle of nowhere
surrounded by donkeys.

1525
01:48:56.363 --> 01:49:01.201
Well. that was our good friend. Galloway.
He's less than pleased.

1526
01:49:01.285 --> 01:49:03.953
How is it that we can't reach our men.

1527
01:49:04.038 --> 01:49:09.417
but he can reach me.
from some random Egyptian desert?

1528
01:49:13.422 --> 01:49:14.672
Nothing.

1529
01:49:15.257 --> 01:49:18.134
Right. go burn an SOS.
Let the eye in the sky know we need some help.

1530
01:49:18.219 --> 01:49:20.220
- Yes. sir.
- Okay. boys. old school time!

1531
01:49:20.638 --> 01:49:22.972
Pop some more flares
so the kid can find us.

1532
01:49:28.729 --> 01:49:32.190
Look. There it is.
We got a couple of miles.

1533
01:49:32.858 --> 01:49:37.695
Lennox's team has the latest
in quantum crypto gear.

1534
01:49:37.780 --> 01:49:43.159
Can somebody tell me why we can't
establish simple radio contact?

1535
01:49:43.244 --> 01:49:45.912
We're hailing them on
every frequency and mode in the book. sir.

1536
01:49:45.996 --> 01:49:48.373
Our satellites in the area have gone blind.
We're working it. sir.

1537
01:49:48.457 --> 01:49:52.085
Damn it. Something's not right.
It doesn't add up.

1538
01:49:52.169 --> 01:49:55.588
Contact the Jordanians.
see what air assets they've got in the area.

1539
01:49:55.673 --> 01:49:58.049
and get Egypt's General Salam.

1540
01:49:58.133 --> 01:50:02.011
Ask him to clear some USV overflights
in Egyptian airspace.

1541
01:50:02.096 --> 01:50:05.181
We need an assist
in confirming visuals now.

1542
01:50:05.432 --> 01:50:07.016
Scramble Predators now.

1543
01:50:07.184 --> 01:50:08.601
V-1. rotate.

1544
01:50:20.656 --> 01:50:22.490
We still have a mile that way.

1545
01:50:28.163 --> 01:50:29.539
Come on.

1546
01:50:32.626 --> 01:50:34.210
This way. This way.

1547
01:50:38.841 --> 01:50:42.176
- One man. alone...
- Stop saying that!

1548
01:50:42.261 --> 01:50:43.511
...betrayed by the country he loves!

1549
01:50:43.595 --> 01:50:45.805
Oh. my goodness.
I'm in the car. okay? You're not alone.

1550
01:50:46.473 --> 01:50:48.975
Just relax.
You're with the maestro.

1551
01:50:57.651 --> 01:50:59.694
I don't think he's still following us.

1552
01:51:00.696 --> 01:51:02.363
That's what you think.

1553
01:51:19.214 --> 01:51:22.967
Master. sorry to be the bearer of bad news.

1554
01:51:23.052 --> 01:51:26.095
but the soldiers brought the body of Prime.

1555
01:51:26.180 --> 01:51:28.389
The boy must have the Matrix.

1556
01:51:28.807 --> 01:51:31.434
We cannot let him reach Optimus.

1557
01:51:32.102 --> 01:51:35.772
Decepticons. begin our assault!

1558
01:51:36.482 --> 01:51:38.107
We've got incoming!

1559
01:51:54.249 --> 01:51:57.168
We got a whole lot of fight
coming our way.

1560
01:51:57.252 --> 01:51:59.253
- How many?
- About 13 of them.

1561
01:51:59.338 --> 01:52:02.006
This ain't good.
This ain't good.

1562
01:52:10.224 --> 01:52:12.433
We're about to get our asses whupped.

1563
01:52:13.560 --> 01:52:15.353
Bravo-Charlie. kneel!

1564
01:52:15.437 --> 01:52:18.314
All right. those Decepticons
are searching for Sam.

1565
01:52:19.691 --> 01:52:22.610
Whatever he has.
he thinks it'll bring Optimus back to life.

1566
01:52:22.694 --> 01:52:25.571
so our mission is to find him
and get him to Optimus.

1567
01:52:25.656 --> 01:52:28.449
All right. we're gonna draw fire from the left flank.
I need a scout team.

1568
01:52:28.534 --> 01:52:29.575
I'm leading.

1569
01:52:29.660 --> 01:52:32.078
Go up through the middle
with Arcee and Ironhide!

1570
01:52:32.162 --> 01:52:33.704
All right. when you see the precious cargo.

1571
01:52:33.789 --> 01:52:36.541
I want you to pop green smoke and
come back through those pillars.

1572
01:52:36.625 --> 01:52:39.836
We'll have the ambush set. All right.
Let's go. Move out!

1573
01:52:49.054 --> 01:52:51.347
You ever see that film
Gunfight at the O.K. Corral?

1574
01:52:52.850 --> 01:52:56.018
- With Burt Lancaster and Kirk Douglas?
- No. why?

1575
01:52:59.273 --> 01:53:02.108
- Looks like we're right in the middle of it.
- Is that good?

1576
01:53:04.319 --> 01:53:05.862
A lot of people died.

1577
01:53:24.089 --> 01:53:25.256
Hide!

1578
01:53:26.717 --> 01:53:28.801
- Vamonos. amigos!
- Oh. my God!

1579
01:53:33.223 --> 01:53:34.724
- Hit the deck!
- Oh. my God!

1580
01:53:50.824 --> 01:53:51.908
Sam. Sam.

1581
01:53:52.993 --> 01:53:55.036
I don't think they saw us.

1582
01:53:55.579 --> 01:53:57.413
Get down. Get down.

1583
01:53:57.789 --> 01:53:59.373
Okay. Listen.

1584
01:54:01.251 --> 01:54:04.587
Once it's clear. we run for Optimus
as fast as we can. okay?

1585
01:54:05.923 --> 01:54:07.423
What if it doesn't work?

1586
01:54:08.258 --> 01:54:09.842
It's gonna work.

1587
01:54:09.927 --> 01:54:12.929
- What if it doesn't?
- It's gonna work. It'll work.

1588
01:55:49.359 --> 01:55:50.818
Up. up. up!

1589
01:56:00.787 --> 01:56:02.455
Get ready to jump!

1590
01:56:21.308 --> 01:56:23.976
We got a half-mile.
I don't think the soldiers know we're here.

1591
01:56:26.688 --> 01:56:28.022
Fall back!

1592
01:56:28.106 --> 01:56:31.525
- Ironhide. up the middle!
- Ironhide. move it!

1593
01:56:31.610 --> 01:56:33.611
Let's go! Go. go!

1594
01:56:40.827 --> 01:56:42.203
Devastator!

1595
01:56:44.665 --> 01:56:46.582
We're trapped! There's nowhere to go.
We're gonna die.

1596
01:56:46.667 --> 01:56:48.918
If we're going out.
we're going out like men. understand?

1597
01:57:19.700 --> 01:57:21.534
Look at this mother...

1598
01:57:21.618 --> 01:57:23.285
Mean robots suck!

1599
01:57:33.922 --> 01:57:36.507
Hang on! Hang on. okay?

1600
01:57:41.638 --> 01:57:43.431
- Simmons!
- Don't let go!

1601
01:57:43.515 --> 01:57:45.975
Hang in there. I got you!
Just hang in.

1602
01:57:49.980 --> 01:57:51.480
I don't want to die!

1603
01:57:53.400 --> 01:57:55.276
Kung fu grip. boy.
Kung fu grip!

1604
01:57:55.360 --> 01:57:56.610
You ain't getting me!

1605
01:58:01.032 --> 01:58:03.325
He dead. He got so ate.

1606
01:58:03.660 --> 01:58:06.579
- Who's your daddy now. huh?
- He got all ate up.

1607
01:58:06.663 --> 01:58:08.789
The only safe place is right under it.

1608
01:58:08.874 --> 01:58:12.543
- Run at it. Run for its feet! Move it!
- Yeah.

1609
01:58:19.426 --> 01:58:22.762
You should've never eaten me!
I'm gonna bust your face up!

1610
01:58:27.768 --> 01:58:28.934
Oh. my God!

1611
01:58:31.688 --> 01:58:34.190
Nobody mess with me!
In your face!

1612
01:58:35.108 --> 01:58:36.776
Keep fighting. Mudflap!

1613
01:58:37.694 --> 01:58:39.028
Oh. my God!

1614
01:58:45.410 --> 01:58:47.369
Nobody messes with the twins.

1615
01:58:50.373 --> 01:58:52.583
I got you... My bad!

1616
01:58:55.337 --> 01:58:57.379
Man! You shot me in the face!

1617
01:58:57.839 --> 01:59:00.132
- Stay under it!
- Yeah. stay under it!

1618
01:59:04.095 --> 01:59:05.387
Come on.

1619
01:59:21.404 --> 01:59:22.571
Judy!

1620
01:59:27.661 --> 01:59:29.745
- Sam! Sam!
- What?

1621
01:59:30.747 --> 01:59:32.706
Sam! Sam!

1622
01:59:37.170 --> 01:59:38.420
Sam!

1623
01:59:38.505 --> 01:59:39.839
- Sam!
- Dad!

1624
01:59:47.597 --> 01:59:48.973
Wait. wait!

1625
01:59:50.225 --> 01:59:53.727
Please listen to me!
I want you to run! Run!

1626
01:59:53.812 --> 01:59:56.522
Dad. just stop!
They don't want you. they want me!

1627
01:59:56.606 --> 01:59:58.065
- Oh. God!
- Wait!

1628
01:59:58.149 --> 02:00:00.025
Sam Witwicky.

1629
02:00:00.110 --> 02:00:04.405
Don't hurt them. This is what you want.
You don't want them.

1630
02:00:04.489 --> 02:00:06.156
- Go! Go!
- Please. stop!

1631
02:00:06.241 --> 02:00:07.408
- Stop!
- Listen to your father!

1632
02:00:07.492 --> 02:00:09.285
Just get out of here!

1633
02:00:09.619 --> 02:00:11.996
Just don't hurt them.
I know what you want.

1634
02:00:12.080 --> 02:00:13.581
Just go! Just go!

1635
02:00:13.665 --> 02:00:17.459
And I know that you need me
because I know about the Matrix.

1636
02:00:18.086 --> 02:00:19.628
- Don't do it. Sam...
- Please. Dad.

1637
02:00:19.713 --> 02:00:23.674
- They're going to kill us all anyway!
- Here's what you want. right here.

1638
02:00:24.050 --> 02:00:25.467
Bumblebee!

1639
02:00:38.690 --> 02:00:40.316
Kill him. Bee.
Kill him.

1640
02:01:18.271 --> 02:01:20.856
- Stay tight. Ma.
- Come on. Get in here.

1641
02:01:34.746 --> 02:01:36.538
- Bee?
- Yeah.

1642
02:01:40.043 --> 02:01:41.126
- Hey!
- I don't know

1643
02:01:41.211 --> 02:01:43.170
what's going on. but we've got to move!

1644
02:01:47.342 --> 02:01:49.218
There's got to be a way out of here!

1645
02:01:50.553 --> 02:01:52.596
Judy. get back. get back.

1646
02:01:53.807 --> 02:01:56.809
Against the wall. 
Against the wall.

1647
02:01:58.186 --> 02:02:00.187
Bee! Bumblebee!

1648
02:02:01.064 --> 02:02:03.023
You get them somewhere safe. all right?

1649
02:02:05.402 --> 02:02:06.527
You've got to get in the car
and get to safety.

1650
02:02:06.611 --> 02:02:08.487
No. this isn't up for discussion!

1651
02:02:08.571 --> 02:02:10.447
- You're my son! You're my son!
- I know.

1652
02:02:10.532 --> 02:02:11.782
- Dad...
- We all go together!

1653
02:02:11.866 --> 02:02:13.158
- Listen...
- We're all going together!

1654
02:02:13.243 --> 02:02:16.537
Dad. stop. okay? Get in the car.
He's gonna get you to safety.

1655
02:02:16.621 --> 02:02:18.872
You know. you run.
You don't stop. you don't hide. you run.

1656
02:02:18.957 --> 02:02:21.542
You hear what I'm saying. okay?
I'll find you when you're safe.

1657
02:02:21.626 --> 02:02:23.127
- No.
- You've got to let me go. Dad.

1658
02:02:23.211 --> 02:02:26.547
- You have to let me go. You have to.
- Ron.

1659
02:02:29.259 --> 02:02:31.677
Ron. Ron. let him go.

1660
02:02:33.722 --> 02:02:36.098
You come back! Come on.

1661
02:02:36.182 --> 02:02:37.933
Ron! Mikaela! Mikaela!

1662
02:02:38.018 --> 02:02:40.561
- Go with my parents.
- I'm not gonna go without you.

1663
02:02:51.865 --> 02:02:53.449
Move to cover!

1664
02:02:57.662 --> 02:02:59.413
We got Jordanians!

1665
02:02:59.497 --> 02:03:00.956
We got help!

1666
02:03:07.088 --> 02:03:08.338
Down!

1667
02:03:24.898 --> 02:03:26.565
You okay. soldier?

1668
02:03:26.649 --> 02:03:29.777
We're gonna help you. soldier.
Let's get these wounded clear of the bird.

1669
02:03:29.861 --> 02:03:31.779
Stay still. Stay still. Don't move.

1670
02:03:31.863 --> 02:03:34.156
You all right. young man?
You have a radio?

1671
02:03:35.617 --> 02:03:40.079
Hey. kid. it's been nice knowing you.
Remember what I did for my country.

1672
02:03:41.581 --> 02:03:43.248
This is my moment.

1673
02:03:44.000 --> 02:03:45.084
You're crazy!

1674
02:03:47.170 --> 02:03:49.046
ETA to station. two minutes.

1675
02:03:49.130 --> 02:03:51.006
- Put it on the main screen.
- Sir. Yes. sir.

1676
02:03:51.091 --> 02:03:52.508
Predator 01.

1677
02:04:02.977 --> 02:04:04.186
Shit. it's a trick.

1678
02:04:04.270 --> 02:04:06.688
Commence Operation Firestorm.
Send everyone.

1679
02:04:06.773 --> 02:04:09.358
- Get those Marines on the ground.
- Roll in strike packages...

1680
02:04:09.692 --> 02:04:11.360
Task Force Ripper. execute Lightning.

1681
02:04:31.840 --> 02:04:34.383
- Spotted Sam!
- Sam!

1682
02:04:34.843 --> 02:04:36.135
Ironhide!

1683
02:04:37.011 --> 02:04:39.179
Follow us to the pillars.
We'll take you to Optimus.

1684
02:04:42.058 --> 02:04:44.685
Get out. Sam!
Get to the pillars!

1685
02:04:45.937 --> 02:04:47.062
Let's go.

1686
02:04:50.733 --> 02:04:54.236
Oh. God. This is it.
The pyramid's built right over the machine.

1687
02:04:54.320 --> 02:04:58.699
If they turn that machine on.
no more sun.

1688
02:05:01.161 --> 02:05:05.581
Not on my watch.

1689
02:05:16.593 --> 02:05:18.093
USS Stennis. Identify.

1690
02:05:18.178 --> 02:05:20.596
Where the hell are you?
Watching the Weather Channel?

1691
02:05:20.680 --> 02:05:22.556
SportsCenter?
I Dream of Jeannie or something?

1692
02:05:22.640 --> 02:05:26.643
We got 300 satellites up there.
Where the hell are all our men?

1693
02:05:26.728 --> 02:05:28.270
Identify yourself.

1694
02:05:28.771 --> 02:05:29.980
What is your name. sailor?

1695
02:05:30.565 --> 02:05:35.527
Wilder. Captain of the USS John C. Stennis aircraft carrier.

1696
02:05:36.863 --> 02:05:38.530
Okay. Captain Wilder.

1697
02:05:38.615 --> 02:05:40.908
This is Agent Seymour Simmons
of Sector 7.

1698
02:05:40.992 --> 02:05:43.368
There is the mother of all non-biologicals

1699
02:05:43.453 --> 02:05:45.245
getting ready to blow up our sun.

1700
02:05:45.330 --> 02:05:47.164
Do you want to have a throwdown
about my lack of clearance

1701
02:05:47.248 --> 02:05:49.291
or do you want to help save
a gazillion lives?

1702
02:05:50.251 --> 02:05:52.628
All right. Agent Simmons.
I'm listening.

1703
02:05:59.802 --> 02:06:02.471
Five clicks west of the Gulf.

1704
02:06:02.555 --> 02:06:05.557
we got ourselves an alien
remodeling a pyramid.

1705
02:06:05.642 --> 02:06:08.644
Our one hope is a prototype weapon
called a Rail Gun.

1706
02:06:08.728 --> 02:06:11.772
- shoots a steel projectile at Mach 7.
- That's classified.

1707
02:06:11.856 --> 02:06:15.442
Don't talk to me about classified.
all right?

1708
02:06:15.526 --> 02:06:18.237
Now. if you've got a battleship in the Gulf.
which I know you do.

1709
02:06:18.321 --> 02:06:20.822
you tell them to ready that weapon!

1710
02:06:22.200 --> 02:06:24.409
Contact destroyer USS KIDD.

1711
02:06:25.286 --> 02:06:26.954
Alpha Team. flank left!

1712
02:06:27.038 --> 02:06:28.830
This way! Move it!

1713
02:06:30.750 --> 02:06:33.001
- Where do you need us. sir?
- Protect those in the line of fire.

1714
02:06:33.086 --> 02:06:34.711
Let's go! Go!

1715
02:06:38.633 --> 02:06:41.134
Give me your Comms.
Come on. Epps!

1716
02:06:45.515 --> 02:06:47.933
Right now. we need air support. ASAP!

1717
02:06:48.017 --> 02:06:50.560
Have troops in contact 20 miles northwest.
Radar contact.

1718
02:06:50.645 --> 02:06:51.770
Proceed to 88 Alpha Sierra...

1719
02:06:55.858 --> 02:06:57.442
B-1. snap 090.

1720
02:06:57.527 --> 02:06:59.945
You are approved to drop your
2.000-pound JDAMs.

1721
02:07:07.161 --> 02:07:08.495
- What you got?
- I couldn't get to them. sir.

1722
02:07:08.579 --> 02:07:10.622
They're 600 meters away
and they're heading right for the pillars.

1723
02:07:10.707 --> 02:07:13.542
All right. Precious cargo's coming!

1724
02:07:13.876 --> 02:07:14.876
Move!

1725
02:07:25.763 --> 02:07:27.306
Curse you!

1726
02:07:41.279 --> 02:07:43.405
Sam! Spotted Sam!

1727
02:08:15.646 --> 02:08:17.397
- Come on!
- 2-2 covering fire.

1728
02:08:17.482 --> 02:08:18.940
Two civilians. 12 o'clock!

1729
02:08:27.450 --> 02:08:29.034
Cover for us!

1730
02:08:35.458 --> 02:08:38.210
Hold the air strike!
We're rescuing civilians!

1731
02:08:50.515 --> 02:08:52.140
Keep firing!

1732
02:08:58.106 --> 02:08:59.773
Come on! Mikaela!

1733
02:09:00.191 --> 02:09:02.526
Come on! Get in here!

1734
02:09:03.486 --> 02:09:04.903
Look who showed up.

1735
02:09:04.987 --> 02:09:06.988
You better have a good reason for us to be here.

1736
02:09:07.073 --> 02:09:08.782
- Where's Optimus?
- He's right over there.

1737
02:09:08.866 --> 02:09:10.325
across the courtyard.

1738
02:09:10.993 --> 02:09:13.328
- I got to get to him right now.
- Not with an air strike coming.

1739
02:09:13.413 --> 02:09:15.664
I have to get to him right now.

1740
02:09:17.166 --> 02:09:18.500
Go. Back. back. back. back.

1741
02:09:18.584 --> 02:09:20.335
- Go.
- Listen up...

1742
02:09:23.756 --> 02:09:24.965
Okay.

1743
02:09:28.594 --> 02:09:29.970
Incoming!

1744
02:09:30.972 --> 02:09:33.181
Stick the landing.

1745
02:09:34.100 --> 02:09:36.977
Behold the glory of Jetfire!

1746
02:09:38.271 --> 02:09:41.857
Now let me show you
how we brought the pain in my day!

1747
02:10:01.878 --> 02:10:03.211
I'm too old for this crap.

1748
02:10:03.379 --> 02:10:06.006
Keep going man. 15 rounds of fighting.

1749
02:10:26.152 --> 02:10:29.654
I am directly below the enemy's scrotum.

1750
02:10:30.406 --> 02:10:33.700
25.7 meters above sea level.
29.32 north.

1751
02:10:33.784 --> 02:10:35.994
- Kill track. 5205...
- Target acquired.

1752
02:10:36.078 --> 02:10:38.663
- Killing track.
- Two. one...

1753
02:10:38.748 --> 02:10:40.081
Fire!

1754
02:10:54.263 --> 02:10:55.889
Yeah! Yeah!

1755
02:10:56.265 --> 02:10:59.935
B-1's time on target. 30 seconds.
2.000-pound JDAMs inbound.

1756
02:11:00.019 --> 02:11:02.145
We're gonna make a break through
the B's on my command. okay?

1757
02:11:02.230 --> 02:11:05.148
You guys stick with me. you understand?
You stay on my ass.

1758
02:11:05.358 --> 02:11:08.610
- 1-1 tally orange smoke.
- I hope these F-16s got good aim.

1759
02:11:08.694 --> 02:11:12.280
- Yeah? Why is that?
- I told them to hit the orange smoke.

1760
02:11:13.824 --> 02:11:15.283
You mean that orange smoke?

1761
02:11:15.368 --> 02:11:16.952
It wasn't my best toss. okay?

1762
02:11:17.036 --> 02:11:19.788
- Viper. thunder.
- Run!

1763
02:11:28.798 --> 02:11:30.090
Incoming!

1764
02:11:33.177 --> 02:11:34.469
Come on!

1765
02:11:54.699 --> 02:11:55.865
Sam!

1766
02:12:03.708 --> 02:12:04.958
Run!

1767
02:12:07.878 --> 02:12:08.962
Die!

1768
02:12:16.012 --> 02:12:17.262
Sam!

1769
02:12:33.487 --> 02:12:35.030
Hold your fire!

1770
02:12:37.408 --> 02:12:38.575
Sam!

1771
02:12:40.202 --> 02:12:42.454
Stay back!
Mikaela. stay back!

1772
02:12:44.540 --> 02:12:46.541
Fucking do something!

1773
02:13:21.911 --> 02:13:28.166
- Sam! Sam!
- Sam! Sam! Sammy! Sam!

1774
02:13:29.960 --> 02:13:31.753
- Let me go!
- Come on. you got to move.

1775
02:13:31.837 --> 02:13:34.631
- You got to move. come on.
- We got no pulse.

1776
02:13:34.715 --> 02:13:35.840
Starting CPR.

1777
02:13:35.925 --> 02:13:39.094
- I have to see my kid! I got a son...
- Sammy!

1778
02:13:39.845 --> 02:13:40.970
Sam!

1779
02:13:43.307 --> 02:13:44.849
- Clear.
- Ready to shock.

1780
02:13:44.934 --> 02:13:47.727
- Clear!
- Ready to shock. One. two. three.

1781
02:13:50.648 --> 02:13:52.107
Do it again!

1782
02:13:57.613 --> 02:13:58.947
No!

1783
02:14:00.950 --> 02:14:06.037
Okay. listen to my voice.
I love you and I need you.

1784
02:14:07.289 --> 02:14:10.875
Please. Please. come back to me.
Sam. please!

1785
02:14:10.960 --> 02:14:12.502
I love you.

1786
02:14:21.887 --> 02:14:26.266
Where am I?
Am I dead?

1787
02:14:26.767 --> 02:14:31.020
We have been watching you
a long. long time.

1788
02:14:33.399 --> 02:14:37.402
You have fought for Optimus.
our last descendant.

1789
02:14:37.486 --> 02:14:42.574
with courage and with sacrifice.
the virtues of a leader.

1790
02:14:43.492 --> 02:14:46.077
a leader worthy of our secret.

1791
02:14:46.662 --> 02:14:51.291
The Matrix of Leadership is not found.
it is earned.

1792
02:14:52.501 --> 02:14:54.711
Return now to Optimus.

1793
02:14:55.421 --> 02:14:57.756
Merge the Matrix with his spark.

1794
02:14:58.340 --> 02:15:02.886
It is. and always has been. your destiny.

1795
02:15:07.850 --> 02:15:08.975
Sam!

1796
02:15:15.441 --> 02:15:17.859
I love you. I love you.

1797
02:15:55.314 --> 02:15:58.691
Boy. you returned for me.

1798
02:15:59.985 --> 02:16:01.945
A living Prime.

1799
02:16:03.572 --> 02:16:05.740
I don't believe it!

1800
02:16:15.793 --> 02:16:18.253
My Matrix!

1801
02:16:23.592 --> 02:16:25.468
Get up! Get up!
Get up! Get up!

1802
02:16:26.387 --> 02:16:27.929
Get up. Prime!

1803
02:16:29.807 --> 02:16:31.182
Oh. no.

1804
02:16:31.559 --> 02:16:35.520
He's turning on the machine!
You got to stop him! Get up!

1805
02:16:36.021 --> 02:16:37.397
Optimus!

1806
02:16:39.608 --> 02:16:41.943
Fallen. my master.

1807
02:16:42.027 --> 02:16:46.489
My brothers could not stop me from this.

1808
02:16:47.408 --> 02:16:51.786
Yes. now I claim your sun.

1809
02:16:54.081 --> 02:16:57.208
- Move!
- Enemy target. top of pyramid. Engage!

1810
02:16:57.293 --> 02:16:58.793
Engage! Engage!

1811
02:17:04.300 --> 02:17:07.218
In moments. we'll be at firing strength.

1812
02:17:22.818 --> 02:17:27.363
All my Decepticon life.
I never did a thing worth doing until now.

1813
02:17:27.907 --> 02:17:30.825
Optimus. take my parts

1814
02:17:30.910 --> 02:17:34.078
and you will have a power
you've never known.

1815
02:17:35.039 --> 02:17:37.081
Fulfill your destiny.

1816
02:17:43.380 --> 02:17:45.214
Jolt!
Electrify!

1817
02:17:45.674 --> 02:17:47.634
Transplant those afterburners.

1818
02:18:05.945 --> 02:18:07.570
Let's roll.

1819
02:18:10.032 --> 02:18:12.116
Fire mission on the pyramids.

1820
02:18:24.004 --> 02:18:27.423
This planet will be dark forever.

1821
02:18:49.655 --> 02:18:52.073
Die. like your brothers!

1822
02:18:52.741 --> 02:18:54.951
They were your brothers. too.

1823
02:19:23.814 --> 02:19:25.690
Starscream!

1824
02:19:38.704 --> 02:19:40.872
You picked the wrong planet.

1825
02:19:43.834 --> 02:19:45.752
Give me your face.

1826
02:19:54.261 --> 02:19:55.928
I rise.

1827
02:19:56.472 --> 02:19:58.056
You fall.

1828
02:20:00.851 --> 02:20:03.311
No. no.

1829
02:20:05.355 --> 02:20:07.774
Not to call you a coward. Master

1830
02:20:07.858 --> 02:20:13.529
but sometimes cowards do survive.

1831
02:20:14.156 --> 02:20:16.115
This isn't over.

1832
02:20:43.811 --> 02:20:46.687
It took all this for you
to tell me that you love me.

1833
02:20:48.273 --> 02:20:49.857
You said it first.

1834
02:21:40.993 --> 02:21:43.619
Thank you Sam.
for saving my life.

1835
02:21:44.913 --> 02:21:46.247
Welcome.

1836
02:21:46.999 --> 02:21:48.749
Thank you for believing in me.

1837
02:21:53.589 --> 02:21:58.092
Our races united by a history long forgotten

1838
02:21:58.177 --> 02:22:01.596
and a future we shall face together.

1839
02:22:02.139 --> 02:22:04.557
I am Optimus Prime.

1840
02:22:04.641 --> 02:22:09.687
and I send this message so that
our pasts will always be remembered

1841
02:22:09.771 --> 02:22:13.649
for in those memories. we live on.

1842
02:22:36.465 --> 02:22:39.342
So glad you could join us.
Professor Einstein.

1843
02:22:39.843 --> 02:22:41.802
Yeah. I was kind of busy.

1844
02:22:44.473 --> 02:22:45.640
Okay.
